FBIS4-12538 "drnes069_r_94013" FBIS-NES-94-069 Daily Report 8 Apr 1994 India D'Souza Reinstalled as Chief Minister of Goa D'Souza Reinstalled as Chief Minister of Goa BK0904074994 Delhi All India Radio Network in English 1530 GMT 8 Apr 94 BK0904074994 Delhi All India Radio Network English BFN [Text] Dr. Wilfred D'Souza has been reinstalled as the chief minister of Goa. He was administered the oath of office and secrecy by the governor, Mr. B. Rachaiah, in Panaji this evening. Five other ministers also took office. They are: Mr. Vasu Paik Gaonkar, Mr. Suresh Parulekar, Mr. Ashok Naik Salgaonkar, Dr. (Karno Pigado), and Mr. Vinay Kumar Usgaonkar. Talking to newspersons after the swearing-in ceremony, the chief minister said he will act according to the wishes of the party high command on the induction of five dissident ministers who resigned last week.
